{"text": "今日はホワイトデーなんですよね！", "character": "IA_時雨Jun様", "emotion": "joy", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "もう、それは先月もやりましたってば！", "character": "IA_時雨Jun様", "emotion": "anger", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "OИEちゃんと二人でお返しを持ってきました！", "character": "IA_時雨Jun様", "emotion": "happiness", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "うわー、嬉しいな、ありがとう。", "character": "琴葉葵_時雨jun様", "emotion": "embarrassment", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "ホワイトデーってもらったものを3倍にして返すんですよね！", "character": "IA_時雨Jun様", "emotion": "joy", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "そんなカウンターパンチを決めるものだっけ、ホワイトデーって。", "character": "琴葉葵_時雨jun様", "emotion": null, "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "またお姉ちゃんから変なこと吹き込まれてー…。", "character": "琴葉葵_時雨jun様", "emotion": null, "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "いえ、今回はOИEちゃんから聞きましたよ？", "character": "IA_時雨Jun様", "emotion": "surprise", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "えっ、意外なところから出てきたな。", "character": "琴葉葵_時雨jun様", "emotion": "surprise", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "いや、わざわざ金額に換算しなくても…。", "character": "琴葉葵_時雨jun様", "emotion": "sadness", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "足りないと思ったら1gずつ\r\nこれで調整するんで…。", "character": "OИE_時雨Jun様", "emotion": "fear", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "足りない分はIAのスマイルで！", "character": "IA_時雨Jun様", "emotion": "joy", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "なんと、笑顔って100万ドルになるらしいですよ！", "character": "IA_時雨Jun様", "emotion": "joy", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "えっ！", "character": "IA_時雨Jun様", "emotion": "surprise", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "そんなぁ…。", "character": "IA_時雨Jun様", "emotion": "sadness", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "知っとるか、ホワイトデーの相場ってもらったもんの3倍なんや！", "character": "琴葉茜_時雨jun様", "emotion": "happiness", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "よし、想像通りの返答やな。", "character": "琴葉茜_時雨jun様", "emotion": "happiness", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "それを探しに行くに決まっとるやん、今から！", "character": "琴葉茜_時雨jun様", "emotion": "happiness", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "相変わらず無計画だぁ。", "character": "紲星あかり_時雨jun様", "emotion": "happiness", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "えー…。", "character": "紲星あかり_時雨jun様", "emotion": "sadness", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "あー…。", "character": "紲星あかり_時雨jun様", "emotion": "sadness", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "あー…。", "character": "IA_時雨Jun様", "emotion": "sadness", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "そーぉ…かも、しれませんね？", "character": "IA_時雨Jun様", "emotion": "sadness", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "あっ。", "character": "IA_時雨Jun様", "emotion": "surprise", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "うにゃっ？", "character": "紲星あかり_時雨jun様", "emotion": "surprise", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "本当？　ありがとう！", "character": "紲星あかり_時雨jun様", "emotion": "joy", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "はい！", "character": "IA_時雨Jun様", "emotion": "happiness", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "えーっと…。", "character": "紲星あかり_時雨jun様", "emotion": "surprise", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "オイ！", "character": "琴葉茜_時雨jun様", "emotion": "surprise", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "あれ、葵さんから教わってたのぉ！？", "character": "紲星あかり_時雨jun様", "emotion": "surprise", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "はい、せっかくならおいしいほうがいいなって。", "character": "IA_時雨Jun様", "emotion": "happiness", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "前のクッキーがおいしかったですし。", "character": "IA_時雨Jun様", "emotion": "happiness", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "たしかにそうだけどぉ！", "character": "紲星あかり_時雨jun様", "emotion": "surprise", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
{"text": "これ、おいしー。", "character": "OИE_時雨Jun様", "emotion": "happiness", "source_project": "ホワイトデー_noneemo.ymmp", "ts": 1780472349.7132316}
